sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Middleware
    participant InfluencerSignInPage
    participant InfluencerSignInForm
    participant Clerk
    participant InfluencerDashboard

    User->>Middleware: Navigates to /sign-in/influencer
    
    alt is user already authenticated?
        alt role === "influencer"
            Middleware-->>User: redirect to /influencer
        else role === "brand"
            Middleware-->>User: redirect to /brand
        end
    else no session
        Middleware->>InfluencerSignInPage: render InfluencerSignInPage
        InfluencerSignInPage->>InfluencerSignInForm: renders InfluencerSignInForm
    end
    
    User->>InfluencerSignInForm: Fills: email, password
    User->>InfluencerSignInForm: Clicks Sign in → handleSignIn fires
    InfluencerSignInForm->>Clerk: signIn.create({ identifier: email, password })
    
    alt error
        Clerk-->>InfluencerSignInForm: returns error
        InfluencerSignInForm-->>User: toast.error shown, flow ends
    else status === "complete"
        Clerk-->>InfluencerSignInForm: returns complete
        InfluencerSignInForm->>Clerk: setActive({ session: createdSessionId })
        Note over InfluencerSignInForm, Clerk: Session active in browser
        InfluencerSignInForm->>User: router.push("/influencer")
        
        User->>Middleware: intercepts /influencer request
        Middleware->>Middleware: checks: userId exists ✓
        Middleware->>InfluencerDashboard: forwards to layout
        InfluencerDashboard->>InfluencerDashboard: layout checks: role === "influencer" ✓
        InfluencerDashboard-->>User: Access granted → dashboard renders
    end
